sdesc: "Video editor designed for simple tasks"
ldesc: "Avidemux is a free video editor designed for simple cutting, 
filtering and encoding tasks. It supports many file types, including 
AVI, DVD compatible MPEG files, MP4 and ASF, using a variety of codecs. 
Tasks can be automated using projects, job queue and powerful scripting 
capabilities."
